---

---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-48 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 bg-zinc-50">
    <div
      class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-zinc-50 via-white to-zinc-100/90 opacity-95"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-200 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative blobs -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-96 h-96 bg-brand-500/10 rounded-full blur-3xl mix-blend-multiply animate-pulse"
    >
    </div>
    <div
      class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-[30rem] h-[30rem] bg-amber-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl mix-blend-multiply animate-pulse"
      style="animation-delay: 2s;"
    >
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h1
      class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-zinc-900 tracking-tight mb-8 animate-fade-in-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.1s;"
    >
      Transformamos tus ideas en<br class="hidden md:block" />
      <span
        class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-900 via-zinc-800 to-brand-600"
        >impresiones de calidad</span
      >
    </h1>

    <p
      class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-lg md:text-xl text-zinc-600 mx-auto mb-10 animate-fade-in-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"
    >
      Descubre nuestras soluciones personalizadas y destaca con nuestro servicio
      excepcional. Expertos en impresión desde cero.
    </p>

    <div
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-4 animate-fade-in-up"
      style="animation-delay: 0.3s;"
    >
      <a
        href="#productos"
        class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 bg-brand-500 text-zinc-900 hover:bg-brand-600 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-brand-500/20 rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm"
      >
        Explorar Servicios
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/573216426377"
        target="_blank"
        class="w-full sm:w-auto px-8 py-4 glass text-zinc-800 border border-zinc-200 hover:bg-zinc-100 rounded-full font-bold transition-all duration-300 flex items-center justify-center gap-2"
      >
        <svg
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          class="h-5 w-5"
          viewBox="0 0 20 20"
          fill="currentColor"
        >
          <path
            fill-rule="evenodd"
            d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-8.707l-3-3a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L10.586 9H7a1 1 0 100 2h3.586l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414l3-3a1 1 0 000-1.414z"
            clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
        </svg>
        Asesoría Gratuita
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @keyframes fade-in-up {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  .animate-fade-in-up {
    animation: fade-in-up 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
    opacity: 0;
  }
</style>
